{"lemma":"ضَجْعَة","slug":"ضَجْعَة","root":"ض.ج.ع","root_slug":"ض-ج-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ج-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25562","n25563","n25564","n25565","n25566"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25562","headword_ar":"ضَجْعَةٌ","root":"DjE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of lying, upon the side"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"otherwise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sleeping:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, O, * TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sleep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weakness"},{"kind":"text","text":"in judgment; (O, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujoEapN","text_ar":"ضُجْعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY raA^oyihi DajoEapN","text_ar":"فِى رَاْيِهِ ضَجْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his judgment is weakness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) ―         -b3-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ease; repose; freedom from"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trouble"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inconvenience, and toil"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujoEapN","text_ar":"ضُجْعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n25563","headword_ar":"ضُجْعَةٌ","root":"DjE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One whom people often lay upon his side"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throw down"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) ―         -b2-  [And app.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who lays others on the side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prostrates them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is implied by what here follows.] ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A disease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) because it lays the man upon his bed. (TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DajoEapN","text_ar":"ضَجْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b5-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujaEapN","text_ar":"ضُجَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n25564","headword_ar":"ضِجْعَةٌ","root":"DjE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of lying upon the side"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any posture"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, O, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sleeping."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sluggishness, laziness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indolence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu DijoEapK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ ضِجْعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDojaEN","text_ar":"مَضْجَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) It is said in a trad. that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DijoEap","text_ar":"ضِجْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the Apostle of God was of skins, (IAth, JM, TA,) stuffed with fibres of the palm-tree: (IAth, TA:) meaning his"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","IAth","JM","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n25565","headword_ar":"ضَجَعَةٌ","root":"DjE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a gen. n. (O, K) in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiDoTijaAEN","text_ar":"اِضْطِجَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lying upon the side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any manner;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleeping"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n25566","headword_ar":"ضُجَعَةٌ","root":"DjE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) and, accord. to the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujoEapN","text_ar":"ضُجْعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this [as an epithet] has the meaning first assigned to it above, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujoEiy~apN","text_ar":"ضُجْعِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DijoEiy~apN","text_ar":"ضِجْعِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujoEiY~N","text_ar":"ضُجْعِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DijoEiY~N","text_ar":"ضِجْعِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) the last two [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DuijoEaY","text_ar":"ضُِجْعَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", but] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEodiY~N","text_ar":"قُعْدِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiEodiY~N","text_ar":"قِعْدِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAjEN","text_ar":"ضَاجعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [or this last is a simple part. n.,] (tropical:)  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who lies upon his side"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleeps,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"often:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sluggish, lazy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indolent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and O in explanation of the first, and K in explanation of all:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who keeps to the house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent; seldom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"never, going forth; nor rising and speeding to do a generous deed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impotent and stationary:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [or,] accord. to IB, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAjiEN","text_ar":"ضَاجِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DujoEiY~N","text_ar":"ضُجْعِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DijoEiY~N","text_ar":"ضِجْعِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is content with his poverty, and betakes himself to his house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]}]}}